entry.title: New release for Rocket.Chat: 7.5.4
entry.content:
Engine versions

  • Node: 22.13.1
  • MongoDB: 5.0, 6.0, 7.0
  • Apps-Engine: 1.50.0

Patch Changes

  • Bump @rocket.chat/meteor version.

  • (#36618 by @dionisio-bot) Fixes a bug where the /api/v1/users.update API call was replacing the entire customFields object instead of merging only the specified properties. The fix ensures that when updating custom fields, existing values are preserved while only specified fields are updated or added.
